cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CV 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with language modeling. It could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it involves the use of deep learning techniques. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it involves the use of neural networks. Finally, it could also be categorized under cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) as character information can be used to recognize patterns in text.
